{
  "stem": "393.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But we, the enemy, had Hitler to keep up the bar with our work.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We worked by the thousands.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We were all over.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I remember once some-- some girls tried to escape, because sometimes, you had to go at nighttime to-- to bring the bread.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And it was dark.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And if somebody wanted, they can-- to-- maybe to-- to get away.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But they brought them back right away.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Our clothes was made in that way-- our coat-- that it has a big patch sewed in in the middle of the back-- sewed in, not painted-- which was in stripes.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So from far away, you could see that this is a prisoner.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They took him back.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They were-- they were punished.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, but very fast.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "First of all, we weren't so many.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In Guben, we were only 1,000 altogether-- altogether.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In Auschwitz, we were 3-- 30,000.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then we had to go.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We had to work.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They-- they-- they counted us every day, going and coming.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But it was-- it was made very, very, very, very fast, so-- because there-- there wasn't time.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We-- we needed some time to sleep, to take a rest.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we needed time to get to the factory in rain, and snow, with our bald heads, you see-- with-- with no stockings, which we-- they just gave us one coat, we had, which was-- whether thin, or-- as it-- as it came out, you know-- not-- not winter-like-- absolutely.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Just we were very young.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In Guben, we-- so nobody died.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was two girls who were sick, and I think they-- they didn't survive the-- the road from Guben.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You see?",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
